# NavigationWizard — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/navigation-wizard.css`

## CSS Classes

### Base
- `.acko-wizard` — flex, items-center, `gap: var(--space-1)`
- `.acko-wizard-vertical` — flex-col, items-start, `gap: 0`
- `.acko-wizard-compact` — compact layout for mobile

### Step
- `.acko-wizard-step` — flex, items-center, `gap: var(--space-2)`
- `.acko-wizard-step-info` — flex-col, `margin-left: var(--space-2)`
- Vertical step: `flex-row items-start`

### Circle
- `.acko-wizard-circle` — `var(--scale-32) × var(--scale-32)`, `border-radius: var(--radius-full)`, flex center, font-weight 600

### Connector
- `.acko-wizard-connector` — `width: var(--scale-40)`, height 2px, flex-shrink-0
- Completed: `--color-success`
- Default: `--color-border-subtle`
- Vertical: `width: 2px`, `height: var(--scale-32)`, margin-left 15px, margin `var(--space-1)` top/bottom

### Compact
- Circle: `var(--scale-24)`, font `--font-label-sm-size`
- Connector: `var(--scale-32)` width
- Label: `--font-caption-size`

### Step States

| Status | Circle BG | Circle Text | Label Color |
|--------|-----------|-------------|-------------|
| Upcoming | `--color-surface-raised-hover` | `--color-text-muted` | `--color-text-muted` |
| Current | `--color-primary` | `--color-on-primary` | `--color-text-strong` |
| Completed | `--color-success` | `--color-on-primary` | `--color-text-strong` |
| Error | `--color-error-text` | `--color-on-primary` | `--color-error-text` |

### Current Step Ring
`box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px var(--color-primary-ring)`

### Labels
- `.acko-wizard-label` — `--font-body-sm-size`, font-weight 500, `--color-text-muted`
- `.acko-wizard-description` — `--font-caption-size`, `--color-text-muted`

### Transitions
All color changes: `200ms ease`

## Dark Theme
Automatic via semantic token remapping.
